<h1>About By Bus</h1>
<p class="Text">
    By Bus is an Egyptian shareholding company working in the field of public transport under the supervision of the Ministry of Transport since 1998.
</p>
<p class="Text">
    It is the first private sector company operating in the area of public transportation.
</p>
<p class="Text">
    By Bus provides technical solutions by using information and communication technology to improve passenger transportation services and works on developing its benefits for the public to simplify their lives.
</p>
<hr />
<img src="~/img/About/Buses.jpg" class="Image"/>
<br />
<p class="TextMid">
    Our Vision
</p>
<p class="TextSamll">
    Our vision is to provide an outstanding service that exceeds the needs and expectations of our customers to become the easiest and safest solution. We always strive to become a leading company in the field of private transport services by providing comfort and luxury to all users of By Bus services.
</p>
<br />
<p class="TextMid">
    Our Mission
</p>
<p class="TextSamll">
    Our mission is to provide convenient and safe transportation services that our customers can rely on as a suitable alternative to vehicles. Therefore, we follow our passengers’ needs to enhance our services. Our principle in By Bus is the comfort and luxury of travelers.
</p>
